 off fae mischief.\n\n====Name origin====\nKlefki is a combination of \'\'clef\'\' (French for key) or a corruption of \'\'kleptomaniac\'\' (in reference to its habit of collecting keys) and \'\'key\'\'.\n\nCleffy is derived from \'\'clef\'\' (French for key).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Steel|type2=Fairy\n|ja=クレッフィ \'\'Cleffy\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'{{tt|clef|French for key}}\'\'\n|fr=Trousselin|frmeaning=From \'\'{{tt|trousseau|keychain}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|gobelin|goblin}}\'\'\n|es=Klefki|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Clavion|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|clāvis|Latin for key}}\'\'\n|it=Klefki|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=클레피 \'\'Keullepi\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of its Japanese name\n|zh_yue=鎖圈兒 \'\'Sóhyūnyìh\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|鎖圈 \'\'sóhyūn\'\'|keyring}} and {{tt|兒 \'\'yìh\'\'|diminutive suffix meaning child}}\n|zh_cmn=鑰圈兒 \'\'Yàoquānér\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|鑰匙圈 \'\'yàoshíquān \'\'|keyring}} and {{tt|兒 \'\'ér\'\'|diminutive suffix meaning child}}\n|hi=क्लेफकी \'\'Klefki\'\'|himeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Клефки \'\'Klefki\'\'|rumeaning=Transliteration of English name\n}}\n{{-}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Steel|type2=Fairy}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Steel|prevnum=706|prev=Goodra|nextnum=708|next=Phantump}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Clavion]]\n[[es:Klefki]]\n[[fr:Trousselin]]\n[[it:Klefki]]\n[[ja:クレッフィ]]\n[[zh:钥圈儿]]'}